# =============================================================================
# Brewfile — curated for clean macOS install
# Lessons baked in from 2026-05-23 reset (see docs/01-lessons-learned.md)
#
# REMINDER: Sign into Mac App Store BEFORE running `brew bundle install` or
# every `mas` line silently skips. There's no error message.
